HEADWORD: Campanula
<hw>Cam*pan"u*la</hw> <pr>(k⟦acr⟧m*p⟦acr⟧n"⟦usl⟧*l⟦adot⟧)</pr>,
<pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[LL. <ets>campanula</ets> a little bell; dim.
